---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions | Grammarly AI Humanizer" 
  description="Review the Terms & Conditions for Grammarly AI Humanizer. Read our usage guidelines, intellectual property ownership terms, and fair use policies."
  canonicalUrl="https://grammarlyaihumanizer.com/terms-conditions/"
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow relative py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Floating Mesh Background -->
    <div class="mesh-backdrop"></div>
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl relative z-10">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-link mb-3 inline-block">Terms of Service</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-[-1px] text-ink mb-4">
          Terms & Conditions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-mute text-xs font-mono">Last Updated: July 2, 2026</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Card -->
      <div class="card-marketing-large bg-canvas border border-hairline p-8 sm:p-12 rounded-lg shadow-sm space-y-8 text-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
        
        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using the website <strong>Grammarly AI Humanizer</strong> (located at <a href="/" class="text-link hover:underline">grammarlyaihumanizer.com</a>), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions, all applicable laws and regulations, and agree that you are responsible for compliance with any local laws. If you do not agree with any of these terms, you are prohibited from using or accessing this site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">2. License and Scope of Service</h2>
          <p>
            Grammarly AI Humanizer provides a web-based utility that modifies text inputs using advanced AI models to adjust structural perplexity and burstiness. We grant you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access the site and use the tool for personal, academic, or commercial writing enhancement purposes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">3. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Your Input Content:</strong> You retain full intellectual property ownership and copyright of all texts, paragraphs, and articles that you input into the Grammarly AI Humanizer tool. We do not claim any rights over your text.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Generated Outputs:</strong> You own the copyright and rights to the humanized texts generated as output. You are free to edit, publish, distribute, or monetize the generated text.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Website Property:</strong> The site design, proprietary scripts, logos, user interfaces, and the underlying humanization engine algorithms are the exclusive intellectual property of Grammarly AI Humanizer and are protected by international copyright laws.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">4. Acceptable Use and Restrictions</h2>
          <p>
            You agree to use our website and tool only for lawful purposes. You are specifically prohibited from:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Using web scrapers, bots, automated scripts, or API emulation tools to submit bulk requests to the site without explicit written authorization.</li>
            <li>Submitting text that contains malware, viruses, phishing payloads, or malicious scripts.</li>
            <li>Inputting materials that violate copyright, intellectual property, or legal rights of third parties.</li>
            <li>Using the service to generate illegal content, defamatory text, hate speech, or harassment.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">5. Fair Use Limits</h2>
          <p>
            To prevent system strain, ensure stable access for all users, and manage server resources:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>We impose character limits per request (as indicated on our main editor interface).</li>
            <li>We enforce rate limits based on IP addresses. Attempts to circumvent these limits via proxies or rotating VPN networks are violations of these terms.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The materials and services on the Grammarly AI Humanizer website are provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis. We make no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaim and negate all other warranties including, without limitation, implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property.
          </p>
          <p>
            Further, we do not warrant or make any representations concerning the accuracy, likely results, or reliability of bypassing 100% of all third-party AI detectors (e.g., Turnitin, GPTZero, ZeroGPT, Copyleaks), as detection methodologies are constantly evolving and subject to changes outside our control.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">7. Limitations of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            In no event shall Grammarly AI Humanizer or its suppliers be liable for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of data or profit, or due to business interruption) arising out of the use or inability to use the humanization tool, even if we have been notified orally or in writing of the possibility of such damage.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">8. Revisions and Errata</h2>
          <p>
            The materials appearing on the website could include technical, typographical, or photographic errors. We do not warrant that any of the materials on its website are accurate, complete, or current. We may make changes to the materials contained on its website at any time without notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms & Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which we operate, and you irrevocably submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in that State or Location.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
